          "sha": "2d07384243c9552aa8e95c80d7a279e2d224a753",
          "html_url": "https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/commit/2d07384243c9552aa8e95c80d7a279e2d224a753"
        }
      ],
      "message": "build: add `bitcoind-release` preset with only `BUILD_DAEMON` enabled with `release` build type\n\nWhen benchmarking IBD or reindex behavior we have to build bitcoind only, which currently looks like:\n  cmake -B build -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -DBUILD_CLI=OFF -DBUILD_TESTS=OFF -DBUILD_TX=OFF -DBUILD_UTIL=OFF -DENABLE_EXTERNAL_SIGNER=OFF -DENABLE_WALLET=OFF -DINSTALL_MAN=OFF\nAfter this change we can simplify that to\n  cmake --preset bitcoind-release",
      "committer": {
